title: CUTE PUPPY CARE
description: Take care of a cute puppy in this adorable girl game! Look it's hurt! Quickly tend to its wounds, give it some medicine and clean its fur. The little dog is already looking much better, but it's very hungry. Give it some tasty food and make it happy again. Finally, you can dress the pet up for a party with its new animal friends. Style it and select a funny costume!
